                      (HELLO.ASM        ):00028         ; These are fixed addresses in the Color BASIC ROM.
                      (HELLO.ASM        ):00029         ; They are indirect jump vectors 芒聙聰 the ROM may change which
                      (HELLO.ASM        ):00030         ; routine they point to between versions, so we use JSR [addr]
